response.overview: “What Would Spider-Man Do?” is a fan film that delves into Peter Parker’s internal struggles with feelings of inadequacy, even as external threats challenge his role as Spider-Man. Directed by Dusty Dale Barker and written by Zachery Gosse, who also portrays Peter Parker/Spider-Man, the film offers a nuanced exploration of the character’s psyche.
response.tagline: Peter Parker battles inner demons of inadequacy as exterior forces threaten to end his role as Spider-Man.
response.title: What Would Spider-Man Do?
